{"tid":1035960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無事啦無事啦，沙利談門將拒換鬧劇：一場誤會","createTime":"2019-02-25T01:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T08:19:53.000Z","uid":1441,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ced10f6ac03ecf4e7b6b3906502c2eec49c418","tid":1035960,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"周日英聯盃發生車路士門將阿列沙巴拿加拒絕被換離場的鬧劇，主帥沙利及當事人阿列沙巴拿加齊聲說成誤會。<br />\n<br />\n周日之戰緊張而不精彩，賽後最多人談論的是阿列沙巴拿加（Kepa Arrizabalaga）在加時拒換離場的鬧劇，為此，領隊沙利說：「我誤會了當時情況，直到隊醫來到教練席才了解。這是一大誤會，我以為門將抽筋而不能在互射12碼把關，但沒有抽筋，可以參與互射12碼。」他表明阿列沙巴拿加不會因此而受罰。<br />\n<br />\n阿列沙巴拿加拒絕被換後，雖然在互射12碼階段救出了利萊辛尼的12碼，但救不了車仔，佐真奴費路和大衛雷斯先後宴客，車仔最終與錦標擦身而過。<br />\n<br />\n談到帥位問題，沙利認為雖然失盃，但一切與賽前情況無異，自信仍得到會方及球員支持：「賽後，我必須說肯定（仍在更衣室內具威信），因為球員踢出我所要求的。今天，我為球員感到自豪。」被追問到拒換風波會否令他帥位更不穩，他答：「你得問會方。」<br />\n<br />\n至於阿列沙巴拿加口徑一致：「我必須說是誤會，沒有片刻企圖不遵從指令，只是醫護兩度入場，他（沙利）以為我沒條件繼續。直到醫護抵教練席前，出現了2或3分鐘誤會。這與我這星期所面對的（腿筋傷）無關。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24693234133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24693234133&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=1b124afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24693234133</a>"},{"pid":"6da56bfc488d1edbcccddcb7649905c651ca8cb9","tid":1035960,"uid":9457,"like":6,"dislike":46,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"又炒車"},{"pid":"ba30bcf7f5f6ef5dec172aa704c200cbd4e5de18","tid":1035960,"uid":168339,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"係真唔係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85f8d74a682bb3b78f61f99a08e68ef85958b8a","tid":1035960,"uid":166785,"like":151,"dislike":0,"score":151,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:43:43.000Z","msg":"誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />煙狗發曬老脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee2187459a0c03a00d446dc3987a224df697aad","tid":1035960,"uid":23707,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"但沒有抽筋，可以參與互射"},{"pid":"1bff18858d9db2ee4f879a558c8054ec7f5d16da","tid":1035960,"uid":36724,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"被誤會"},{"pid":"c1a7916f07f93e4567257dd34dc5eb0aaf9b03e9","tid":1035960,"uid":39133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"無誤會呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"6ed7f41ebc04a8bdb088de5d198b68234389d52d","tid":1035960,"uid":5649,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:49:52.000Z","msg":"沙利得罪教練都可以無事？車仔班球員真係大晒"},{"pid":"fab891c25cda43ea2b2ae9e63d69b0d1bd1bec00","tid":1035960,"uid":160592,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"90d13f39da621d3b63849d9a9d30363d5c2077c4","tid":1035960,"uid":86272,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:51:50.000Z","msg":"球証誤會所以舉牌"},{"pid":"dbd817c2f511442686563b355ba9d5d1a7ce11d1","tid":1035960,"uid":86272,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"90d13f39da621d3b63849d9a9d30363d5c2077c4","tid":1035960,"uid":86272,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:51:50.000Z","msg":"球証誤會所以舉牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:52:23.000Z","msg":"卡巴誤會所以行出黎熱身"},{"pid":"63cc1c46349354bcf28a3400e85d8259fa6b6350","tid":1035960,"uid":36372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:53:52.000Z","msg":"卡巴尼路守十二碼勁喎"},{"pid":"a9a58fa99b6aff5dbf196640302bff89dcbb1dcb","tid":1035960,"uid":119778,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"沙利擺明圍護住kepa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm